anger has grown along with the number of palestinian attacks on 
their settlements during the 9monthold uprising which has killed 
four israelis and nearly 260 arabs 
on sunday 200 settlers protested outside government offices 
where the cabinet was discussing whether to allow them to open fire 
more freely on the stonethrowers authorities have said civilians 
may open fire only when their lives are in imminent danger 
military jeeps escort local buses on their way through 
palestinian towns and refugee camps sites of frequent 
rockthrowing attacks and soldiers patrol the areas but many 
