provide a mandatory death penalty against those who commit 
murder in the course of a federal drug felony one liberal 
democratic alternative calls for mandatory life imprisonment 
allow admission in court of improperly seized drug evidence if 
law enforcement officers acted in good faith 
deny student loans fha mortgages rent subsidies and other 
