disdain by walking out minutes before the vote the vote by a show 
of hands came on the opening day of the trades unions weeklong 
annual conference in bournemouth england 
the electronic telecommunication and plumbing union was ousted 
for signing two singleunion nostrike pacts with management in 
violation of trades union policy under such agreements a plants 
work force is represented by a single union and disputes are 
settled by arbitration 
the trades union policy is that such contracts weaken union 
bargaining power and lead to competition among unions for 
representation in a shrinking job market 
