in the complexity of the involvements of different layers of 
government and governmental authority the complexity of the number 
of litigants claimants and participants 
all the major brokerage firms were involved the bond rating 
agencies were involved bond counsel were involved and different 
engineering firms accounting firms as well as all layers of 
government he said 
those complexities aside however and the case comes down to 
who will pick up the tab for the wppss default and the ensuing 
